## 🔒 Bulletproof Gate Verification (Pre-Check)

**Before verifying PRD implementation, check bulletproof artifacts:**

```typescript
// Bulletproof pre-verification
const bulletproofCheck = {
  traceabilityMatrix: await fileExists('/docs/flows/TRACEABILITY-MATRIX.md'),
  zeroOmissionCert: await fileExists('/docs/flows/ZERO-OMISSION-CERTIFICATE.md'),
};

if (bulletproofCheck.zeroOmissionCert) {
  const cert = await readFile('/docs/flows/ZERO-OMISSION-CERTIFICATE.md');
  
  // Verify the PRD's screens are in the certificate
  const prdScreens = extractScreensFromPRD(prdId); // From PRD's "Screens" section
  
  for (const screen of prdScreens) {
    if (!cert.includes(screen)) {
      console.warn(`⚠️ Screen "${screen}" from PRD not found in Zero Omission Certificate`);
      console.warn('   This screen may have been missed during flow design (Step 4)');
    }
  }
  
  // Check certificate shows zero gaps
  const hasZeroGaps = cert.includes('Features WITHOUT Screens | 0') ||
                      cert.includes('Screen Omission Gap | 0');
  
  if (hasZeroGaps) {
    console.log('✅ Bulletproof verification: All screens accounted for');
    addBonusPoints(5); // Bonus for bulletproof compliance
  }
}
```

**Bulletproof Bonus Points:**
- +5 points if Zero Omission Certificate exists and shows 0 gaps
- +3 points if TRACEABILITY-MATRIX.md exists
- +2 points if WIREFRAME-TRACKER.md exists

