## 🎯 Success Criteria

**Minimum Score:** 8/10 to pass

**Scoring:**
- Phase 1-10: 1 point each (10 points total)
- Phase 11.5 (Wireframes): Bonus +10 points if Step 5 prototypes exist
- Red flags: -5 points each

**Final Grade:**
- **9-10:** ✅ PRODUCTION READY - Ship it
- **8:** ✅ PASS - Minor polish needed
- **6-7:** ⚠️ NEEDS WORK - Fix gaps before shipping
- **<6:** ❌ FAIL - Major rework required

